OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778771468
OL,3,CRapist who attacked schoolgirl wearing
OL,4,Cuniform jailed
OL,6,FA rapist who picked up a schoolgirl in
OL,7,Fher school uniform on the street
OL,8,Fbefore attacking her has been jailed.
OL,10,FOmarie Adams, 34, approached the 13-
OL,11,Fyear-old in daylight on 11 September
OL,12,Flast year and drove her to multiple
OL,13,Flocations around Leeds, where he
OL,14,Fsexually abused her over two hours.
OL,16,FHe was identified after giving the
OL,17,Fvictim his phone number.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
