FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778771468
OL,3,CRapist who attacked schoolgirl wearing
OL,4,Cuniform jailed
OL,6,FDuring a three-day trial at Leeds
OL,7,FCrown Court, he claimed he had not
OL,8,Fnoticed the victim was wearing her
OL,9,Fschool jumper.
OL,11,FAdams, of Second Avenue, Armley, was
OL,12,Ffound guilty of four counts of rape as
OL,13,Fwell as sexual assault.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for 13 years, with an
OL,16,Fextended licence period of seven years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
