FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778771468
OL,3,CRapist who attacked schoolgirl wearing
OL,4,Cuniform jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement to the court the victim
OL,7,Fsaid: "I have recurring thoughts that
OL,8,FI am useless. This is because I
OL,9,Fbelieve the suspect saw me as some
OL,10,Fcheap tat on the road that he could do
OL,11,Fwhatever he wanted with. This is
OL,12,Fsomething I overthink about a lot.
OL,14,F"I have supported this investigation
OL,15,Fbecause I want the suspect to be
OL,16,Flocked away so that he faces justice
OL,17,Fand knows he cannot get away with what
OL,18,Fhe has done and won't go on to do this
OL,19,Fto someone else.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
