OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778771468
OL,3,CRapist who attacked schoolgirl wearing
OL,4,Cuniform jailed
OL,6,F"Omarie Adams has taken away my
OL,7,Fdignity. This is not something I will
OL,8,Fever get back. I hope he rots in
OL,9,Fprison."
OL,11,FDet Con Ellie Middlemass, of West
OL,12,FYorkshire Police, said: "Adams
OL,13,Fsubjected a vulnerable young girl to
OL,14,Fhours of atrocious abuse, and this has
OL,15,Funderstandably had a significant
OL,16,Fimpact on her life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]tD@YOU
